{"tid":1846882,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"政府用獅子山精神呃港豬打工仔送死未？","createTime":"2020-01-27T18:43:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T19:03:47.000Z","uid":173326,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"04179ea99cd8690b3f1b91db8537e5d9dd5f610b","tid":1846882,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:43:10.000Z","msg":"廢老、老闆一向鍾意鬧啲識計數嘅打工仔唔捱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例牌內容：後生仔唔好計較眼前得失、唔好怕蝕底、老闆會見到你嘅努力<br />\n<br />\n留名睇政府新嘅維穩宣傳片呃港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e9eeea591283cc37178f8059c61c70e5ad1d15","tid":1846882,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:44:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[事關重大請廣傳]</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人以及醫護、海關等要職唔一齊三罷嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護同海關全家在內嘅更多人<br />\n<br />\n我會支持三罷，亦會身體力行一齊三罷保護香港，直至港府落實封關<br />\n<br />\n大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「感染的人越多越好」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aMf1RYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaMf1RYs.jpg&h=d189414d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「我活不了，你們都別想活」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLMVDM.jpg&h=058fd92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「要死一起死」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46aa09f7b92725531844a8eeec55efdcf51882ef","tid":1846882,"uid":258345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:45:00.000Z","msg":"啲老細大粒既獅子山精神左 下屬就唔需要啦<br />\n根本就係射波"},{"pid":"60feee228520b4de3f1d9cbcdee9608586cd17f4","tid":1846882,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46aa09f7b92725531844a8eeec55efdcf51882ef","tid":1846882,"uid":258345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:45:00.000Z","msg":"啲老細大粒既獅子山精神左 下屬就唔需要啦<br />\n根本就係射波"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:46:57.000Z","msg":"呃啲啱啱出嚟做野、滿腔熱血嘅員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d636e89ea8d4b58f350eb580de5efac4b75adb96","tid":1846882,"uid":17859,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:48:26.000Z","msg":"成班嬰兒潮賤種食哂經濟急速增長年代<br />\n之後重想後生做班狗閪嘅奴隸？<br />\n由班狗閪照返工惹埋肺炎死柒就啱"},{"pid":"de70353b22d473d21a7b0b8afe73fd9ad2531473","tid":1846882,"uid":235727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:49:06.000Z","msg":"獅子山精神其實代表窮鬼頂硬上"},{"pid":"3b3ff4df41ca12bb08cfe0620d9bfc6602e26405","tid":1846882,"uid":235025,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:51:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2e5a1183f6ffba4e906fefd01dbe0b168afabca","tid":1846882,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:51:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73316ae28722bc21de63dce96ab61c1a2c649c5d","tid":1846882,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de70353b22d473d21a7b0b8afe73fd9ad2531473","tid":1846882,"uid":235727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:49:06.000Z","msg":"獅子山精神其實代表窮鬼頂硬上"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:51:53.000Z","msg":"窮剩條命，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852ae49498f3b7b90e77105f42f587cca9218969","tid":1846882,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:52:29.000Z","msg":"我希望大家同我一齊嗌!! 嗌到大陸都一齊嗌!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"htt